					<li>Carry out the verification of data through an accredited independent verifier.</li>

					<li>Once the verification is completed and if the result is positive, the organization must present to the Program Administrator (CAATEEB) all the necessary documentation and in accordance with the established models: DAPcons<sup>®</sup> verification report and report of ACV.</li>

					<li>Registration of the DAPcons<sup>®</sup> in the official registry of the Program, upon payment of the corresponding fee.</li>
					</ol>
